                        <condition key="deficient">The Ms. is damaged by rodents (e.g., <locus target="#27">27</locus>, 30, 118).
 Both boards are broken, the
                           front one has been repaired.
 The sewing is severely damaged. Leaves
                           are held together by means of one-stiched repairs. Some leaves are
                           stained with wax (e.g., <locus target="#3v">3v</locus>, 10v, 42v, 84r).
                           Some leaves are misplaced, some are probably missing.
 Tear amended
                           on <locus target="#20">20</locus>, 116.</condition>
